Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of Spatio-Temporal Affordances (STA) to improve task execution capabilities of an autonomous robot, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also mentions the encoding of action semantics related to the environment, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of Spatio-Temporal Affordance Maps (STAM) involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the application of this framework to support the execution of robot tasks involves control systems (cs.SY).
